eu.ubitech.futuretpm.messages

Class SuccessMessages

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.ubitech.futuretpm.messages.SuccessMessages

  • public class SuccessMessages
extends java.lang.Object
    The SuccessMessages class is containing the various success messages of the app: This class includes 6 fields: {registerSuccessMsg, authenticationSuccessMsg, sealTokenSuccessMsg, unsealTokenSuccessMsg, restCallSuccessMsg, lastTransactionSuccessMsg}

    a constructor SuccessMessages()

    a setter and a getter method for each field {getAuthenticationSuccessMsg(), setAuthenticationSuccessMsg(String), getRegisterSuccessMsg(), setRegisterSuccessMsg(String), getSealTokenSuccessMsg(), setSealTokenSuccessMsg(String), getUnsealTokenSuccessMsg() setUnsealTokenSuccessMsg(String), getRestCallSuccessMsg(), setRestCallSuccessMsg(String), getLastTransactionSuccessMsg(), setLastTransactionSuccessMsg(String)}
